pageContext.claim: “Thanks to our efforts -- there are 2,000 -- thank you. There are 2,000 more Medicare Advantage plans today than there were three years ago.”
pageContext.analysis: There are certainly more Medicare Advantage plans in 2020 than every before -- 3,148. But Trump hypes the number. The gain since 2017 is a little over 1,000 plans, not 2,000, according to the Kaiser Family Foundation. In 2009, there were about 2,800 plans.
